{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_011UwCd6Wg4Brwz5GkFfYtKt","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n### Migration Summary\n\n**Frameworks involved:** Spring Boot 3.3.7 -> Jakarta EE 10 (Open Liberty 26.0.0.2)\n\n**High-level actions performed:**\n- Replaced Spring Boot with Open Liberty as the application server\n- Replaced Spring Data JPA repositories with Jakarta Persistence `EntityManager` API\n- Replaced Spring DI annotations (`@Autowired`, `@Service`, `@Component`) with Jakarta CDI (`@Inject`, `@ApplicationScoped`, `@Singleton`)\n- Replaced Spring `@Transactional` with Jakarta `@Transactional`\n- Replaced Spring Boot auto-configuration with explicit Jakarta EE config files (`persistence.xml`, `beans.xml`, `web.xml`, `faces-config.xml`, `server.xml`)\n- Added JAX-RS REST endpoints for API access\n- Converted packaging from JAR (Spring Boot executable) to WAR (deployed to Liberty)\n- Generated and executed 27 smoke tests - all passing\n\n**Overall outcome:** SUCCESS\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Spring Boot parent/deps with jakarta.jakartaee-api:10.0.0, WAR packaging, liberty-maven-plugin\n- Dockerfile: Multi-stage build with Open Liberty runtime instead of Spring Boot\n- .dockerignore: Updated for new build structure\n- src/main/java/com/example/orderspring/OrderApplication.java: JAX-RS @ApplicationPath replacing @SpringBootApplication\n- src/main/java/com/example/orderspring/service/OrderService.java: @ApplicationScoped + EntityManager replacing @Service + Spring Data repos\n- src/main/java/com/example/orderspring/service/DataInitializationService.java: @Singleton @Startup replacing @Component @EventListener\n\nAdded:\n- smoke.py: 27 smoke tests for REST API endpoints\n- src/main/java/com/example/orderspring/rest/OrderResource.java: JAX-RS REST endpoints\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml: JPA persistence unit configuration\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml: CDI bean discovery configuration\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml: JSF servlet mapping\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/faces-config.xml: JSF navigation rules\n- src/main/liberty/config/server.xml: Open Liberty server configuration\n- src/main/webapp/*.xhtml: XHTML files copied to WAR standard location\n- CHANGELOG.md: Complete migration log\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/com/example/orderspring/repository/CustomerOrderRepository.java\n- src/main/java/com/example/orderspring/repository/LineItemRepository.java\n- src/main/java/com/example/orderspring/repository/PartRepository.java\n- src/main/java/com/example/orderspring/repository/VendorPartRepository.java\n- src/main/java/com/example/orderspring/repository/VendorRepository.java\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Spring Boot config no longer needed\n\nUnchanged:\n- All entity classes (already using jakarta.persistence.*)\n- src/main/java/com/example/orderspring/web/OrderManager.java (already using jakarta.* CDI/Faces)\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n\n- **Errors encountered:** 2 during initial deployment\n  - H2 datasource URL format error (`properties.h2.embedded` -> `properties URL=\"jdbc:h2:mem:...\"`)\n  - Wrong Open Liberty feature names (`jpa-3.1` -> `persistence-3.1`, `ejb-4.0` -> `enterpriseBeans-4.0`, `jaxrs-3.1` -> `restfulWS-3.1`)\n- **Resolution:** Fixed server.xml configuration, rebuilt and redeployed\n- **Final result:** 27/27 smoke tests passing, application fully functional"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":509,"cache_read_input_tokens":119250,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":509,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":943},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a3e41a8f-87c2-49bd-995b-2b11c28e9d8b","uuid":"45242b3b-dd0a-4e74-b9ae-cf393d5e0d7f"}
